      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like a trap. like no matter what i do, it just gets worse. they post stuff about me and i cant even fight back because then i just look like the crazy one. it feels like there is no way out of this. it's just constant. i just want the noise to stop.",
