      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are people to talk to but they dont get it. they just tell me to \"hang in there\" or \"ignore them\" like that actually fixes anything. it doesnt fix the fact that i feel like i'm disappearing. everything is just... so loud and so much. i just want to find a way to make it all stop forever. is that even a thing? just to finally have some peace?",
